data.description: You won't believe the view out the back of this four bedroom beauty that is less than a year old! Because this corner lot home sits on a street that doesn't go all the way through, it provides more privacy than your average house in a subdivision.  The home is barely lived in and has no shortage of upgrades!  Inside you will find a shiplap gas fireplace, walk in tile shower, extended kitchen island, as well as white kitchen cabinets.  Beautiful light colored luxury vinyl plank flooring runs throughout the main living spaces and hallways with carpet in the bedrooms.  This popular floor plan provides a three car garage, open kitchen and living room areas for easy entertainment, a walk in pantry, and the primary bedroom on the opposite side of the house as the spare bedrooms.  Perhaps the biggest appeal of this home in particular is the peaceful view out the back from the covered patio.  Don't wait to schedule your showing!
